high_descs: Turn left, and then go towards the fridge.
Open the fridge and pick up the spoon from the bottom shelf.
Take it to the sink on your left.
Put the spoon in the sink, rinse the spoon, and pick it back up.
Turn around, take a step towards the sink behind you, and then turn back around.
Place the spoon on the left side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: The goal is to wash the spoon and let it dry on the sink.

high_descs: go straight turn left to reach the fridge.
Pick up the spoon on the cupboard.
Turn left to reach the sink on your right.
Put the spoon into the sink and pour the water and clean the spoon.
Take the cleaned spoon from the sink and turn around.
Place the spoon near to the sink.
anns.task_desc: Pick the cleaned spoon and put the spoon near to the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the fridge to your left
Take out one spoon from the bridge
Move to your left to reach the sink
Put the spoon into the sink, wash it and pick it back up
Turn around and go to the sink again
Place the spoon into the sink countertop
anns.task_desc: Place the clean spoon into the sink countertop
